; Regression test for issue #851
; The error handling infrastructure (throw_ macro using thread-local
; _desc_buffer) previously caused undefined symbol errors with certain
; compilers.  This test exercises both normal operation and error paths
; to verify these symbols are properly linked.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal Expenses
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
end test

test bal --limit "!!!" -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing value expression:
  !!!
   ^
Error: ! operator not followed by argument
end test
